name: Warhead IV Limited Edition
additionalNotes: The 601 La Bomba Warhead series debuted in 2013 and has become a semi-regular release, with the fourth installment now arriving at stores in the five years since its debut. An offshoot of the 601 La Bomba line, it is designed to be a bit stronger with a more potent binder and filler, and the use of a Connecticut broadleaf maduro wrapper as opposed to a Nicaraguan habano leaf found on the regular 601 La Bomba.
